Tuple_left_delim.documentation:
Left delimiter of a Tuple type and also instance. Example:

* `[Integer, String]` - a tuple type;
* `[3, "Quixote"]` - a tuple.

EXPR_LEAF.documentation:
Meta-type representing one of:

* a manifest constant of any primitive type;
* a path referring to a value in the archetype;
* a constraint;
* a variable reference.
